text: "Rhiannon" is a 1976 song by British American band Fleetwood Mac and taken from their 10th studio album Fleetwood Mac. It went to number 4 in Canada, number 11 in the United States, number 13 in Australia, number 16 in the Netherlands and number 46 in the United Kingdom when it charted in 1978. == References == Category:1976 songs Category:Blues rock songs Category:Soft rock songs Category:Fleetwood Mac songs
